// Listing 7 from the paper: (min,+) convolution that benefits from super-isospeed optimizations.
// Reference: Zippo, "Super-Isospeed" (2026), doi:10.1145/3793250
// Run with: nancy-playground run listing-7-super-isospeed.mppg

f1 := stair(3, 13*4, 3*17)
f2 := stair(7, 19*15, 12*21)
g := f1 * f2
plot(f1, f2, g)
